1
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,200
In this world,

2
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,760
there's not much fairness to go around.

3
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:16,280
I really did have a great master.

4
00:01:17,239 --> 00:01:18,680
If it weren't for my master,

5
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:21,000
I'd probably be just like you,

6
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,040
sinking deep in the swamp.

7
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:25,760
Mr. Xiao,

8
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,640
which company is your master at now?

9
00:01:32,359 --> 00:01:33,719
He fell seriously ill later

10
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,640
and took early retirement.

11
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:36,879
Oh,

12
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,760
Yifan, still working late?

13
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,359
Master.

14
00:01:45,799 --> 00:01:47,400
I'll leave once I finish the drawings.

15
00:01:48,439 --> 00:01:49,439
After this project wraps up,

16
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,000
I'll recommend you to

17
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:51,959
a real estate company.

18
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:53,879
Really?

19
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:55,680
You're bringing me into real estate?

20
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:57,359
Would I lie to you?

21
00:01:58,359 --> 00:01:59,359
In a little over a month,

22
00:01:59,359 --> 00:02:00,200
I'll be retiring.

23
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:02,159
You're heading into a new industry.

24
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,959
Work hard and build your career.

25
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,120
I have faith in your abilities.

26
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,520
Mr. Xiao,

27
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:15,479
in our line of engineering work,

28
00:02:16,039 --> 00:02:17,199
there are so many temptations out there.

29
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:18,599
Whenever something comes up,

30
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:20,639
I often silently remind myself,

31
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,840
you must have a moral bottom line.

32
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,039
Mr. Xiao,

33
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:28,759
I've let you down.

34
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:29,879
And I've let President He down too.

35
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,120
I'm truly despicable.

36
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,520
But I had my reasons.

37
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,680
I come from the countryside.

38
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:58,240
My father passed away

39
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:58,960
when I was very young.

40
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,879
My mom put me through college alone.

41
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,599
After I graduated, my Uncle Han Lin

42
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:06,199
got me a job at Wanhe Real Estate.

43
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:07,680
Just when I thought

44
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,840
I'd never have to worry about life again,

45
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,759
my mom fell ill.

46
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:13,199
I had to bring her along with me,

47
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,240
running between the site and the hospital.

48
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,319
The medical bills

49
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,960
were truly suffocating me.

50
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:25,120
I really didn't want it to be this way.

51
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,360
But what could I do?

52
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,080
Everything costs money.

53
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,840
I couldn't just watch

54
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,280
my mom die from her illness!

55
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,360
It was my Uncle

56
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,280
and Fang Bing who did this.

57
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:38,439
They forced me into it.

58
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,159
With this money,

59
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:49,000
I can pay for my mom's treatment.

60
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,240
This won't work, Uncle.

61
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,879
You useless fool.

62
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:01,919
This money's enough for you to run.

63
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:04,439
Tomorrow, I'll make sure he can't set foot

64
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,840
inside Wanhe Real Estate.

65
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,560
Are you even human?

66
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:20,959
Junjie treated you so well,

67
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,319
and this is how you repay him?

68
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:24,920
Mr. Xiao,

69
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,920
can I beg President He for forgiveness?

70
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,639
Get the hell out!

71
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,399
I'm sorry, Mr. Xiao.

72
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,639
I really never intended

73
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,720
to have President He killed.

74
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,439
I told the driver too,

75
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,439
to control the gas pedal.

76
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,839
Make sure nothing goes wrong.

77
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,040
Just scare him, that's all.

78
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,879
Did you ever think

79
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,439
what if you actually killed him?

80
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:42,800
Come on, come on.

81
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:55,040
Who are you? What do you want?

82
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:56,319
Lady,

83
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,959
we're not human traffickers.

84
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:58,879
We're not going to

85
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:00,040
harvest your organs.

86
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,160
As long as you cooperate,

87
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:03,839
this will be over soon.

88
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,600
Do you even know

89
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,680
that kidnapping is a crime?

90
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:10,560
Mommy, I'm scared.

91
00:05:10,759 --> 00:05:12,319
Daddy! Hurry, call Daddy!

92
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,319
Auntie,

93
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:16,279
did we run into bad people?

94
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:18,120
Who the hell are you? What do you want?

95
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:19,399
Lady,

96
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,480
as long as you meet

97
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,600
our boss's demands,

98
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:23,000
everything can be worked out.

99
00:05:23,639 --> 00:05:24,279
Who's your boss?

100
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,360
Let me talk to him.

101
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:28,879
You're not qualified to talk to the boss.

102
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,199
However,

103
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,720
your husband is.

104
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,959
He Junjie just got into a car accident,

105
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,720
and the kids and I have been kidnapped.

106
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:38,600
It seems

107
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:39,920
this is a conspiracy against Xiao Yifan

108
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,000
and He Junjie.

109
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,040
I can't panic.

110
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:43,120
Stay calm.

111
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:44,560
Stay calm.

112
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,759
I must protect the children.

113
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,120
Mister,

114
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:55,519
You...

115
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:56,319
Why did you kidnap

116
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:57,480
my little brother and sister?

117
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,399
What does a brat like you know?

118
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,040
Scram!

119
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,079
Go play somewhere else.

120
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,600
This kid sure is nosy.

121
00:06:14,439 --> 00:06:15,000
Boss,

122
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,560
The job's done.

123
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,759
What's the next step?

124
00:06:18,079 --> 00:06:19,120
Your faces

125
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:20,720
have been seen by the woman and the kids.

126
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,120
Once Li Yao arrives,

127
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,000
disappear immediately.

128
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,040
Remember this clearly:

129
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:26,399
If you get caught, you take the fall yourselves.

130
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:27,720
Understood?

131
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:29,759
Got it, got it.

132
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:31,279
When is Li Yao coming?

133
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,439
There are tons of cameras on the road.

134
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,079
When you grabbed them,

135
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,120
didn't you avoid the cameras?

136
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:37,399
Of course we avoided them.

137
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,279
But the license plate definitely got caught.

138
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:40,439
Boss,

139
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:42,800
My wife and I risk our lives for you.

140
00:06:42,959 --> 00:06:43,879
You can't shortchange us.

141
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,040
The money's already been transferred.

142
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,839
Once Li Yao arrives,

143
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,199
disappear immediately.

144
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:50,720
Okay, okay, okay.

145
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:08,680
Hello?

146
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,639
Li Yao,

147
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:10,800
Where are you off having fun, kid?

148
00:07:11,439 --> 00:07:12,160
I'm at

149
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,560
a food stall grabbing a bite.

150
00:07:14,079 --> 00:07:15,160
Who are you with?

151
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,279
No one.

152
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:17,000
Just me.

153
00:07:17,319 --> 00:07:18,199
Get to the scenic area right now,

154
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:19,560
to that empty little cabin.

155
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,439
Keep a close watch on them.

156
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,600
People?

157
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,120
What people?

158
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,360
Why do I have to watch them?

159
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:26,560
Li Yao, you listen to me carefully.

160
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,480
You're the one who had He Junjie hit.

161
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,000
If I go down, you go down with me.

162
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,920
I've kidnapped Xiao Yifan's wife

163
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,360
and He Junjie's kid.

164
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,480
Now go and keep a tight watch on them.

165
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:35,839
What?

166
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,800
You kidnapped Mr. Xiao's wife and kid?

167
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,240
Have you lost your mind?

168
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:39,920
You...

169
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:41,680
Fang Bing,

170
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,040
what the hell are you trying to do?

171
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,720
Xiao,

172
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,959
you listen to me carefully.

173
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,639
Your wife and kid

174
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:48,720
are now in my hands.

175
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,160
If you dare block me from winning the bid,

176
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:51,920
I guarantee they

177
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,959
won't see tomorrow's sun.

178
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:54,519
If you dare call the police,

179
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,199
I'll kill her right now.

180
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:57,959
Fang Bing,

181
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,279
if you dare lay

182
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:00,480
a single finger on them,

183
00:08:00,759 --> 00:08:02,000
I will never let you get away with it.

184
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:21,120
No sign of Yang Hui or the kids.

185
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,439
Where did Fang Bing hide them?

186
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:25,680
Strange. Could they have been moved?

187
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,480
In such a short time?

188
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:30,319
Fang Bing isn't that clever.

189
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:31,680
They must still be nearby.

190
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:38,559
Stop staring at your phone.

191
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:40,039
Your wife's right here. Drink up.

192
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:43,000
He's been out for two hours now.

193
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,799
Even if something held him up,

194
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:46,519
he'd at least text me.

195
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:49,000
Maybe something's holding him up?

196
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,759
Maybe he went home to check on the kids.

197
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:53,200
Hurry, call Yang Hui.

198
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:56,360
You don't trust Yang Hui with the kids?

199
00:08:56,559 --> 00:08:57,440
It's not that.

200
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,039
I just have a heavy heart.

201
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:02,080
Just call already!

202
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,720
Fine, fine.

203
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:16,759
Hey!

204
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:17,399
What are you doing?

205
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:18,120
Are you crazy?

206
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:19,480
Something's wrong.

207
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,240
Something's happened to Xiao Yifan.

208
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:23,840
Maybe his phone's dead?

209
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,559
Go check on Yang Hui's place, quick.

210
00:09:25,879 --> 00:09:27,720
What about you?

211
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,320
I'm just injured, not dead.

212
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,480
Hurry up and go!

213
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,720
Go!

214
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,279
If anything's off, call the police.

215
00:09:33,279 --> 00:09:33,759
Okay.

216
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:39,639
Lady,

217
00:09:39,639 --> 00:09:41,279
quit struggling.

218
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:43,360
It's no use fighting it.

219
00:09:44,759 --> 00:09:46,200
I need to call my husband.

220
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,320
No way.

221
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:49,320
Then...

222
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:51,759
let me take the kids to the bathroom.

223
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,480
And get them something to eat.

224
00:09:54,159 --> 00:09:56,240
You're not going anywhere.

225
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,279
Don't worry.

226
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,600
We won't run.

227
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,879
But you can't make us hold it forever.

228
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,799
The kids are so hungry they can't breathe.

229
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,960
If you let them starve to death,

230
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,440
you'll be executed.

231
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,799
Executed, you understand?

232
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:11,639
Don't try to scare me.

233
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,600
I'm not scaring you.

234
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,440
We live under the rule of law.

235
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,600
There are cameras everywhere.

236
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,559
The price of crime is high.

237
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:21,440
You have kids too, right?

238
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,080
Ma'am,

239
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:28,080
please let my little brother and sister go.

240
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:31,600
If you let us go,

241
00:10:31,919 --> 00:10:33,840
I promise we won't call the police.
